3
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:06,950
Madam Man,

4
00:01:08,070 --> 00:01:09,040
I've come to see you.

5
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:16,230
Back when my dad abandoned us,

6
00:01:17,590 --> 00:01:19,350
I had only you and my mom by my side.

7
00:01:23,150 --> 00:01:24,560
To both me and my mom,

8
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:27,710
you had long been like our closest family.

9
00:01:32,070 --> 00:01:33,200
Eighteen years ago,

10
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:35,120
I should have drowned in that river,

11
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,590
but you...

12
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,120
you were the one who saved me.

13
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,870
When I lost my mom,

14
00:01:48,510 --> 00:01:52,120
you took me in and raised me as if I were your own son.

15
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,230
Xing,

16
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:55,280
what's on your mind?

17
00:01:56,350 --> 00:01:57,070
Madam Man.

18
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,710
I made your favorite pigeon soup for you.

19
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,480
Madam Man,

20
00:02:04,820 --> 00:02:06,510
I'm cold and scared.

21
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:07,920
I miss my mom.

22
00:02:09,480 --> 00:02:10,390
Don't be afraid.

23
00:02:11,110 --> 00:02:12,240
I'm here with you.

24
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,960
I'll stay by your side,

25
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:18,110
and I won't let those bad people hurt you again.

26
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,150
I'll protect you.

27
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:21,320
Madam Man,

28
00:02:21,430 --> 00:02:23,200
I will be strong.

29
00:02:23,430 --> 00:02:25,150
I want to grow up quickly,

30
00:02:25,550 --> 00:02:26,800
so I can protect myself

31
00:02:27,550 --> 00:02:28,960
and you.

32
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,270
Xing,

33
00:02:30,800 --> 00:02:31,670
you're such a good boy.

34
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:35,640
I hope you grow a heart

35
00:02:35,870 --> 00:02:38,110
as tough as stone,

36
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:41,430
so no one can ever hurt you again.

37
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,040
When you grow up,

38
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,150
you must avenge your mother.

39
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,360
Now, drink your soup

40
00:02:47,990 --> 00:02:48,990
before it gets cold.

41
00:02:55,590 --> 00:02:56,240
Madam Man,

42
00:02:57,830 --> 00:02:58,870
to me,

43
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,920
