49
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,150
This vengeance

50
00:03:34,670 --> 00:03:35,960
will not end until justice is served.

51
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,480
I will make them pay

52
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:46,550
for what they've done.

53
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:48,390
Madam Man,

54
00:03:50,480 --> 00:03:52,390
I swear I will avenge you.

55
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,870
Zixing!

56
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:17,960
Zixing,

57
00:04:18,270 --> 00:04:19,470
