67
00:05:02,910 --> 00:05:06,680
She has been watching over me from above.

68
00:05:07,230 --> 00:05:08,910
Take care of yourself,

69
00:05:09,150 --> 00:05:11,680
and don't make us worry about you.

70
00:05:15,910 --> 00:05:18,000
I was wrong for so many years.

71
00:05:19,230 --> 00:05:20,710
For those who are gone,

72
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:24,270
