73
00:05:25,910 --> 00:05:27,120
I was wrong.

74
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:33,560
From now on, don't let those who are gone cause you

75
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:36,000
to neglect those still by your side.

76
00:06:06,060 --> 00:06:09,300
[Ward 2]

77
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,120
Please get better soon.

78
00:06:42,270 --> 00:06:44,440
I won't stop you from doing what you want to do anymore.

79
00:06:45,080 --> 00:06:46,830
